snippet.title: The Plague - Steam Trailer
snippet.description: The Plague is a True FPS action game set in a medieval themed fictional world. Online multiplayer, Team Objective game. Build, Heal, Siege, Burn, Destroy, Kill and Defend! 2 factions, 4 classes and lots of infected. Play as Archer, Crusader, PlagueDoctor or Blacksmith.
